<%=
  render partial: "partials/page_title",
         locals: {
             model_object: nil,
             page_title: "Apply for £3,000 to £10,000"
         }
%>

<h1 class="govuk-heading-xl nlhf-!-line-height-1-3">
  Apply for a grant of<br>
  &pound;3,000 to &pound;10,000
</h1>

<p class="govuk-body">Use this service to:</p>

<p class="govuk-body">Apply for funding from the National Lottery Heritage fund for your heritage project</p>

<%= form_tag(
    url: :funding_application_start,
    method: :put,
    local: true
  ) do |f| 
%>

  <%= render(
      ButtonComponent.new(
        element: "button",
        is_start_button: true,
        text: t("buttons.labels.start_now")
      )
    ) 
  %>

<% end %>

<h2 class="govuk-heading-m">We will ask</h2>

<ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet" aria-label="a list of questions we will ask">

  <li>Questions to find out if your project fits our funding criteria</li>
  <li>What your project will do</li>
  <li>Which of our outcomes your project will achieve</li>
  <li>How much your project will cost</li>

</ul>

<h2 class="govuk-heading-m">You will need</h2>

<ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet" aria-label="a list of things you will need">
  <li>A bank account for your organisation</li>
  <li>A constitution, or governing document, for your organisation</li>
</ul>

<h2 class="govuk-heading-m">Before you start</h2>

<p class="govuk-body">Read about <a class="govuk-link"
                                    href="https://www.heritagefund.org.uk/funding/check-what-we-fund"
                                    aria-label="more detail about what we fund" target="_blank">what we fund</a>
  in more detail</p>

<p class="govuk-body">Learn what we mean by <a class="govuk-link"
                                               href="https://www.heritagefund.org.uk/funding/outcomes"
                                               aria-label="more detail about project outcomes"  target="_blank">project outcomes.</a>
  Outcomes are what we will assess your application against when making a funding decision</p>

<p class="govuk-body">You might find it helpful to refer to our <a class="govuk-link"
                                                                   href="https://www.heritagefund.org.uk/publications/application-guidance-ps3000-ps10000"
                                                                   aria-label="more information on application guidance" target="_blank">Application Guidance</a>
  when answering the questions in this form</p>